  <md:abstract><para id="para-00001">By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para>
<list id="list-00001">
<item>Discuss six fundamental activities of the digestive system, giving an example of each</item>
<item>Compare and contrast the neural and hormonal controls involved in digestion</item>
</list></md:abstract>
